{
  "_doc": "Axis config for the competitive map. Owner-editable. A fork's /setup overwrites this for its own market. score_axes.py reads it; positions are computed, never hand-placed. Keys in *_up/*_down are regexes (case-insensitive) matched against what+why_tier. The defaults below are market-agnostic archetype signals — /setup MUST rewrite the axis labels and signal regexes in YOUR market's vocabulary, and keep cluster keys in step with config/clusters.json (the sync rule in setup.md).",
